 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 | FusionLibServer provides a solution to process data from both OCS    |
 | agents and Fusion agents.                                            |
 | Users can easily retrieve data from these agents with hooks system.  |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+

- You have to correctly complete:
configs.ini,
FusInvHooks.class.php

- Give enough permission to www-data (apache) to write and read on data directory for inventory(default data in configs.ini)

- URI Server: /path/to/FusionLib/main.php

